## Step 1 — See existing ESY EQUITY rows first

```sql
SELECT ds.diffusion_schedule_id,
       ds.diffused_data,
       ds.diffused_filename,
       ds.missing_filename,
       ds.schedule_expression,
       ds.schedule_frequency,
       ds.schedule_time,
       ds.is_active,
       cr.client_label,
       ir.instrument_label
FROM own_83650_muse.muse_diffusion_schedules ds
JOIN own_83650_muse.muse_client_reference cr
    ON ds.client_reference_id = cr.id
JOIN own_83650_muse.muse_instrument_reference ir
    ON ds.instrument_reference_id = ir.id
WHERE cr.client_label = 'ESY'
AND ir.instrument_label = 'EQUITY'
AND ds.is_active = true;
```

